sentiment over with your music.

1025
01:08:10,119 --> 01:08:12,485
- Public sentiment?
- Yes.

1026
01:08:14,323 --> 01:08:16,223
Let me tell you something,

1027
01:08:16,292 --> 01:08:17,418
we're not really interested

1028
01:08:17,493 --> 01:08:19,654
