I believe the mountain people
will be seen

1032
01:08:28,404 --> 01:08:29,803
in a very different light.

1033
01:08:29,872 --> 01:08:32,705
Oh, what is that light,
may I ask?

1034
01:08:32,775 --> 01:08:34,572
Well, the common view

1035
