should never be disassociated.

1176
01:17:32,681 --> 01:17:34,148
The music and text

1177
01:17:34,216 --> 01:17:37,117
are one and indivisible,

1178
01:17:37,185 --> 01:17:38,812
and to separate one
from the other

1179
