this afternoon?

1196
01:18:42,517 --> 01:18:45,350
I haven't had any luck.
Perhaps you might.

1197
01:18:48,156 --> 01:18:49,714
What, and leave her work?

1198
01:18:51,893 --> 01:18:54,225
Deladis, are you ready?

1199
01:18:54,296 --> 01:18:55,786
Um...

1200
01:18:58,633 --> 01:19:00,100
